1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:04,000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 19]

5
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:13,220
Let disciples of both sects

6
00:01:13,270 --> 00:01:15,010
patrol nearby isles

7
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,140
to root out dangers.

8
00:01:16,550 --> 00:01:18,780
Humans and spirits coexist here.

9
00:01:19,750 --> 00:01:22,340
Shen, do not let your guard down.

10
00:01:32,470 --> 00:01:33,140
Tongzhou?

11
00:01:33,880 --> 00:01:36,060
They say Wuyue Court's techniques are unparalleled.

12
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:37,620
Let me see your moves.

13
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:40,620
I'd also like to see Xingzheng Hall's fire-control skills.

14
00:01:55,110 --> 00:01:55,810
Ye Ye?

15
00:01:56,670 --> 00:01:58,010
The streets are crowded with prying eyes.

16
00:01:58,470 --> 00:01:59,620
Why not find a quieter place to spar?

17
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:08,370
Since we meet again after so long,

18
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,780
let's find a place for tea instead.

19
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:11,810
Changyue!

20
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:13,850
You're all here.

21
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:15,970
We just got here.

22
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:19,250
So you're here for the Shanhai Gathering?

23
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:20,900
Only you lot

24
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,410
would dare pick a fight

25
00:02:22,830 --> 00:02:23,850
right in front of Wanxian Sect.

26
00:02:25,870 --> 00:02:26,410
Let's go.

27
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:27,570
We'll talk at the inn.

28
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,500
- Okay. - Let's go.

29
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:29,780
- Go. - Go.

30
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,020
We haven't seen each other in so long.

31
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:31,620
It's been a while.

32
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,090
We should catch up properly.

33
00:02:33,110 --> 00:02:33,500
Sure.

34
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:35,560
[Duanming City Inn]

35
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:42,940
Thanks.

36
00:02:43,270 --> 00:02:44,740
Right this way.

37
00:02:46,110 --> 00:02:47,410
One bite

38
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,020
and I'd break a tooth.

39
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,340
This is called huluo.

40
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,370
The shell

41
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:58,570
only dissolves in acid.

42
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,090
The vinegar soaks into the meat.

43
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:02,340
Add a bit of lime juice when you eat it.

44
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:03,740
Makes it even more flavorful.

45
00:03:05,430 --> 00:03:07,220
Tongzhou, you're so knowledgeable.

46
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,060
You even know this.

47
00:03:09,550 --> 00:03:10,810
Duantu may not be by the sea,

48
00:03:11,150 --> 00:03:13,500
but we keep all kinds of delicacies from the wilds in stock.

49
00:03:14,270 --> 00:03:15,220
Come to Yue State sometime,

50
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:17,060
and I'll treat you to a feast every meal.

51
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,180
Oh,

52
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:22,340
Xiuyuan,

53
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,850
I heard you ran into Yecha

54
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:26,130
at White Cliff?

55
00:03:27,990 --> 00:03:30,500
Is Yecha really as savage as the legends say?

56
00:03:33,270 --> 00:03:35,130
Just a demon spirit from 500 years ago.

57
00:03:35,390 --> 00:03:36,130
Nothing to fear.

58
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,530
Five hundred years ago,

59
00:03:37,670 --> 00:03:39,570
the immortal sects scattered his soul.

60
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,370
This time will be no different.

61
00:03:46,270 --> 00:03:46,940
Jiang.

62
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,220
Your Highness.

63
00:03:56,990 --> 00:03:57,530
What's the matter?

64
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,180
By master's orders,

65
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,970
Wuyue Court disciples will rest briefly.

66
00:04:08,270 --> 00:04:10,340
In two days, we'll head out with Sea Sect disciples

67
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:11,690
to search for demon traces.

68
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,410
This place is close to the East Sea,

69
00:04:13,670 --> 00:04:15,090
and the customs here differ from those in the Central Plains.

70
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:15,980
Disciples

71
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,770
must watch their words and actions.

72
00:04:18,350 --> 00:04:20,210
Avoid conflict with other sects.

73
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:22,420
You should remember to watch

74
00:04:23,350 --> 00:04:24,660
your words and actions too, Qin.

75
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:39,740
Qin, you're leaving?

76
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:46,940
Well, Lifei?

77
00:04:47,470 --> 00:04:48,690
Did that snake give you any trouble?

78
00:04:48,910 --> 00:04:49,620
Trouble?

79
00:04:51,470 --> 00:04:53,500
Let me introduce you.

80
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:55,770
This is my best senior brother at Wuyue Court,

81
00:04:55,910 --> 00:04:56,500
Deng Xiguang.

82
00:04:58,910 --> 00:05:00,060
Deng, let me introduce you too.

83
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:01,860
These are all my friends from the academy.

84
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:03,010
Ji Tongzhou.

85
00:05:03,390 --> 00:05:03,940
And

86
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:04,860
Ye Ye.

87
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:05,860
Changyue.

88
00:05:08,470 --> 00:05:09,860
You said Qin Yangling is a snake?

89
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:11,180
He wronged Lifei?

90
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:12,810
Far worse than that.

91
00:05:13,030 --> 00:05:13,980
He almost had her

92
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,300
branded as a demon spy.

93
00:05:16,270 --> 00:05:17,370
What happened?

94
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:21,590
[Duanming City Inn]

95
00:05:21,590 --> 00:05:22,740
Wuyue Court is clearly

96
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:23,810
covering for him!

97
00:05:24,230 --> 00:05:25,300
How can you just let that slide?

98
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:26,420
No way.

99
00:05:26,710 --> 00:05:28,250
I'm going to teach Qin Yangling a lesson right now.

100
00:05:29,350 --> 00:05:30,300
Alright.

101
00:05:30,910 --> 00:05:32,250
Once I've mastered my skills, I'll...

102
00:05:33,030 --> 00:05:34,300
I'll beat him black and blue!

103
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,130
I'll show him

104
00:05:35,150 --> 00:05:36,740
I'm no pushover.

105
00:05:39,150 --> 00:05:40,420
Ye Ye and the others have already turned in.

106
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,370
You should get some rest too.

107
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:43,450
Lifei!

108
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,130
What's going on

109
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,540
with you and Xiuyuan?

110
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:56,980
He's saved me a few times.

111
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,330
So

112
00:06:00,230 --> 00:06:01,130
you've forgiven him?

113
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,890
Do you remember The Ten Forbidden Arts of Sorcerers?

114
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,500
That ancient book from Qingqiu?

115
00:06:10,230 --> 00:06:11,620
Before going to the Altar of Martyrs,

116
00:06:12,590 --> 00:06:14,690
he used a puppet spell to transfer my injuries to himself.

117
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:19,210
So he never really wanted to hurt you?

118
00:06:22,470 --> 00:06:23,540
Back at Wuyue Court,

119
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,980
I yelled at him, drove him away,

120
00:06:26,590 --> 00:06:27,370
and even hurt him.

121
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:29,370
But he kept protecting me,

122
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:31,420
afraid I'd be in any danger.

123
00:06:32,710 --> 00:06:33,540
My master said

124
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:37,060
nothing in this world can outlast time.

125
00:06:38,230 --> 00:06:39,130
We need to learn to let go.

126
00:06:43,030 --> 00:06:43,540
Forget it.

127
00:06:44,230 --> 00:06:44,810
Let's not talk about him.

128
00:06:45,350 --> 00:06:47,660
I heard you took first place in the Achillea Bead Tournament.

129
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:48,810
Impressive.

130
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:52,010
Actually, I owe it to your Chiyan Stone.

131
00:06:55,230 --> 00:06:56,450
Xiuyuan let me have the win.

132
00:06:58,880 --> 00:06:59,540
I'm going to my room.

133
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:11,100
Lifei is getting prettier.

134
00:07:11,710 --> 00:07:12,890
Even prettier than the princess.

135
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:14,890
Your Highness,

136
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:17,450
you're noble and distinguished.

137
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,180
Lifei's eyes are glued to you

138
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,130
whenever she sees you.

139
00:07:20,790 --> 00:07:21,890
She definitely has a crush on you.

140
00:07:22,150 --> 00:07:22,660
No doubt about it.

141
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:25,060
Back then, you were all young.

142
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:26,210
But now...

143
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:26,860
Alright.

144
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:27,450
- Well... - Enough.

145
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:30,890
Why are you carrying a box?

146
00:07:32,910 --> 00:07:34,060
You said Lifei loves

147
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:34,980
shiny golden things.

148
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,660
And you had me prepare all this gold jewelry

149
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:38,420
and magical treasures.

150
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:39,690
Should I still give them to her?

151
00:07:50,350 --> 00:07:50,860
Lifei,

152
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:53,180
I'd like to talk to you.

153
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:55,810
About what?

154
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:00,940
If...

155
00:08:03,590 --> 00:08:04,660
If I really am Yecha,

156
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,660
would you kill me?

157
00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:11,060
You're not Yecha.

158
00:08:13,470 --> 00:08:14,740
You were just possessed by Yecha.

159
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:18,100
I'm not even sure.

160
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,130
How can you be so certain?

161
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,740
Yecha is hideous.

162
00:08:24,230 --> 00:08:25,060
How could you be him?

163
00:08:27,710 --> 00:08:28,250
Lifei.

164
00:08:31,350 --> 00:08:32,420
Appearances can be changed.

165
00:08:33,110 --> 00:08:33,780
Enough.

166
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,380
I said you're not, so you're not.

167
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:36,450
No arguing with me.

168
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,730
No matter what happened before,

169
00:08:43,870 --> 00:08:44,780
you are Lei Xiuyuan.

170
00:08:45,830 --> 00:08:46,490
You were,

171
00:08:47,590 --> 00:08:48,260
and you always will be.

172
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:55,260
Alright.

173
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:57,900
Remember,

174
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:00,210
no matter who I am,

175
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:04,090
I will never hurt you.

176
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,280
[Duanming City Inn]

177
00:09:23,470 --> 00:09:23,850
Lifei.

178
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:25,020
Let's go.

179
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:26,090
I'll take you somewhere.

180
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:27,490
I haven't had breakfast yet.

181
00:09:27,510 --> 00:09:28,260
There'll be good food.

182
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:28,940
Wait,

183
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:29,850
where are we going?

184
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,210
I used the Vast Blink

185
00:09:32,710 --> 00:09:34,450
to have the imperial chefs of Duantu palace make this meal.

186
00:09:35,470 --> 00:09:36,490
Vast Blink?

187
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,140
What treasure?

188
00:09:53,110 --> 00:09:53,610
Tongzhou,

189
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:56,330
are you some kind of wealth bringer?

190
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,210
So much gold.

191
00:10:00,060 --> 00:10:00,610
Like it?

192
00:10:01,350 --> 00:10:02,020
Catch it!

193
00:10:02,230 --> 00:10:03,610
- Stop! - Catch it!

194
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:04,140
Stop!

195
00:10:04,470 --> 00:10:05,090
Catch it!

196
00:10:05,110 --> 00:10:06,210
Dig out its brain!

197
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:08,120
[Shi Chengtian, Jin, Guangsheng Faction]

198
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:13,490
Who are you?

199
00:10:14,060 --> 00:10:15,780
Dare to cause trouble on Guangsheng Faction's turf?

200
00:10:16,110 --> 00:10:16,780
None of your business!

201
00:10:30,830 --> 00:10:31,260
Tongzhou,

202
00:10:31,630 --> 00:10:32,060
what's wrong?

203
00:10:35,110 --> 00:10:35,780
Get them!

204
00:10:36,220 --> 00:10:36,660
Go!

205
00:10:40,350 --> 00:10:40,660
Let's go!

206
00:10:50,220 --> 00:10:50,780
Keep running.

207
00:10:51,220 --> 00:10:54,900
All of Duanming City is my turf.

208
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:56,610
Where do you think you can run off to?

209
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:01,090
Lifei.

210
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:04,180
Gelin.

211
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:06,180
Shi Chengtian,

212
00:11:06,820 --> 00:11:08,660
these two are guests of Wanxian Sect.

213
00:11:08,990 --> 00:11:10,380
You're harassing them in the street.

214
00:11:10,420 --> 00:11:11,260
What do you mean?

215
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:12,850
Whoever they are,

216
00:11:13,340 --> 00:11:14,420
messing with my business

217
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:17,260
is breaking Duanming City's rules!

218
00:11:17,830 --> 00:11:19,450
Even if Mr. Shen himself showed up,

219
00:11:20,230 --> 00:11:21,540
it wouldn't change a thing.

220
00:11:21,870 --> 00:11:22,900
They just got here.

221
00:11:22,940 --> 00:11:23,690
What rules did they break?

222
00:11:24,110 --> 00:11:25,970
They injured Guangsheng Faction's people!

223
00:11:27,060 --> 00:11:28,780
You were the ones torturing a spirit creature

224
00:11:28,820 --> 00:11:29,690
and trying to take its brain alive!

225
00:11:33,340 --> 00:11:34,540
Duanming City has a strict ban

226
00:11:35,110 --> 00:11:36,260
on torturing spirit creatures.

227
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,810
You knowingly broke the law.

228
00:11:39,350 --> 00:11:40,570
Do you want to get run out of the East Sea?

229
00:11:42,460 --> 00:11:42,970
Misunderstanding.

230
00:11:43,590 --> 00:11:44,210
A misunderstanding.

231
00:11:44,870 --> 00:11:46,060
We weren't torturing a spirit creature.

232
00:11:46,590 --> 00:11:47,540
They saw it wrong.

233
00:11:48,110 --> 00:11:50,380
We were just disciplining

234
00:11:50,990 --> 00:11:52,490
an unruly spirit companion.

235
00:11:53,470 --> 00:11:54,610
I won't bother you further.

236
00:11:54,830 --> 00:11:55,330
I'm leaving.

237
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:56,610
I'll be going.

238
00:11:57,460 --> 00:11:57,850
Let's go.

239
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:58,420
Mr. Shi,

240
00:11:59,340 --> 00:12:00,450
we're just... leaving like that?

241
00:12:01,100 --> 00:12:02,330
Do you know who that guy is?

242
00:12:02,470 --> 00:12:02,940
Who?

243
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:05,140
He's the lord of the seventy-six islands of the East Sea.

244
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:07,540
Cross him, and you'll get nothing but trouble.

245
00:12:08,350 --> 00:12:08,810
Let's go.

246
00:12:08,990 --> 00:12:09,450
Go.

247
00:12:14,350 --> 00:12:15,610
Lifei.

248
00:12:18,590 --> 00:12:19,300
How have you been?

249
00:12:20,100 --> 00:12:21,020
Not bad.

250
00:12:22,870 --> 00:12:23,380
Gelin.

251
00:12:24,590 --> 00:12:26,330
What happened to Tongzhou's eyes?

252
00:12:48,830 --> 00:12:49,380
How is he?

253
00:12:49,630 --> 00:12:50,180
Is he alright?

254
00:12:50,990 --> 00:12:51,450
Nothing serious.

255
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:52,260
Just some scale powder.

256
00:12:52,710 --> 00:12:54,260
A few days of rest and he'll recover.

257
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:55,730
That's good.

258
00:12:57,870 --> 00:12:59,260
Thank you, Gelin's senior brother.

259
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:03,780
That's not his name.

260
00:13:04,710 --> 00:13:05,420
He's Lu Li.

261
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:06,540
Lu,

262
00:13:07,590 --> 00:13:08,570
this is my sister, Changyue.

263
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:11,610
And this is Ye.

264
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:13,020
Lu,

265
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:15,180
Gelin can be quite willful.

266
00:13:15,590 --> 00:13:16,570
Thanks for looking out for her.

267
00:13:17,350 --> 00:13:17,780
No worries.

268
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:19,380
Gelin is my junior sister.

269
00:13:19,710 --> 00:13:20,380
I should look out for her.

270
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,420
I need to report the Guangsheng Faction incident

271
00:13:24,660 --> 00:13:25,660
to my master.

272
00:13:26,540 --> 00:13:27,180
I'll be going.

273
00:13:43,280 --> 00:13:44,180
Lu, take care.

274
00:13:44,540 --> 00:13:45,380
I'll come find you later.

275
00:13:49,750 --> 00:13:50,210
Gelin,

276
00:13:50,710 --> 00:13:52,260
how does a sect like Guangsheng Faction

277
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:53,850
exist in the East Sea?

278
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:56,180
Guangsheng Faction has always been tyrannical.

279
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:57,810
They treat beasts as their property.

280
00:13:57,830 --> 00:13:58,780
They are absolutely ruthless.

281
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:00,300
Out of respect for sect boundaries,

282
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:02,330
my master can't just step in,

283
00:14:02,830 --> 00:14:03,780
even if he hates it.

284
00:14:04,830 --> 00:14:06,090
That Shi guy

285
00:14:06,630 --> 00:14:07,730
seemed really afraid of Lu Li.

286
00:14:08,630 --> 00:14:09,850
The Lu family is a major power in the East Sea.

287
00:14:10,160 --> 00:14:11,660
They own the surrounding islands.

288
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:13,660
Of course Shi Chengtian is wary.

289
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:14,900
Gelin.

290
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:18,730
Does the Sea Sect treat spirits and beasts

291
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:19,540
the way Guangsheng Faction does?

292
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,060
Wanxian Sect isn't like that.

293
00:14:22,470 --> 00:14:24,140
We have a pact with the spirit creatures.

294
00:14:24,350 --> 00:14:25,490
We've

295
00:14:25,510 --> 00:14:26,940
lived in peace for centuries.

296
00:14:27,630 --> 00:14:29,140
But recently,

297
00:14:29,560 --> 00:14:31,180
some spirit creatures have been acting strangely.

298
00:14:32,750 --> 00:14:34,540
Are demons stirring trouble in the shadows?

299
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:38,900
Strange how?

300
00:14:39,590 --> 00:14:41,810
Duanming City has been seeing many

301
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:42,810
unknown spirit creatures

302
00:14:42,830 --> 00:14:44,180
from nowhere.

303
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,420
I heard Guangsheng Faction caught a few.

304
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:49,260
And the spirits and beasts in the city have been losing control too.

305
00:14:50,830 --> 00:14:51,940
Is this connected to the Sea Calamity?

306
00:14:55,280 --> 00:14:56,690
My master said

307
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:58,330
that when the Sea Calamity comes,

308
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:01,450
seawater will pour into Guixu,

309
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:04,090
connecting the Central Plains to the lands beyond.

310
00:15:04,510 --> 00:15:07,060
Many spirits and beasts will flood into the Central Plains.

311
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:10,940
Maybe there's a link.

312
00:15:14,110 --> 00:15:17,180
Is the strange behavior of the spirit creatures really tied to demons?

313
00:15:26,710 --> 00:15:27,970
Your eyes are hurt.

314
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,730
Don't go out to sea tomorrow.

315
00:15:33,510 --> 00:15:34,540
Open your eyes and look.

316
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:38,060
Can you see?

317
00:15:50,830 --> 00:15:51,300
What's wrong?

318
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:55,210
Do they still hurt?

319
00:15:57,830 --> 00:15:58,330
No.

320
00:15:59,920 --> 00:16:01,060
I just suddenly realized

321
00:16:02,110 --> 00:16:03,300
it's not so bad being blind.

322
00:16:05,560 --> 00:16:06,090
That way,

323
00:16:07,990 --> 00:16:09,540
you'd have to keep holding my hand

324
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:12,300
and never leave me.

325
00:16:37,350 --> 00:16:37,810
Well,

326
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:38,610
don't worry.

327
00:16:39,110 --> 00:16:40,300
I won't abandon you.

328
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:42,300
Get some rest. Don't be scared.

329
00:17:02,710 --> 00:17:03,850
You're here to see him too?

330
00:17:10,550 --> 00:17:11,290
I just saw him.

331
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:12,050
Um,

332
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:13,490
go ahead.

333
00:17:13,750 --> 00:17:14,290
See you tomorrow.

334
00:17:22,470 --> 00:17:23,820
I never planned to let her go.

335
00:17:26,510 --> 00:17:27,530
And I never will.

336
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:29,730
Neither will I.

337
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:32,100
Then let's each rely on our own skills.

338
00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:33,940
Deal.

339
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:41,010
Gelin.

340
00:17:42,230 --> 00:17:43,290
Do you have a crush on Ye Ye?

341
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:50,450
You know?

342
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:53,250
Back when you cried at the academy,

343
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:54,820
I didn't understand.

344
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:57,010
But then you suddenly came to the East Sea.

345
00:17:58,470 --> 00:17:59,530
I think I get it now.

346
00:18:01,790 --> 00:18:02,250
So,

347
00:18:02,270 --> 00:18:03,450
does that make me pitiful?

348
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:07,210
You've always been smart and optimistic.

349
00:18:08,340 --> 00:18:09,690
Why not learn to let go?

350
00:18:10,510 --> 00:18:11,490
I want to.

351
00:18:12,840 --> 00:18:13,940
But for all these years,

352
00:18:14,710 --> 00:18:15,290
Changyue,

353
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:16,340
Ye,

354
00:18:16,710 --> 00:18:17,450
and I

355
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:19,050
have been family.

356
00:18:19,510 --> 00:18:20,900
I always tried to be

357
00:18:21,270 --> 00:18:23,580
Changyue's obedient sister

358
00:18:24,710 --> 00:18:27,940
and the girl Ye worried about.

359
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:29,860
But it's so hard.

360
00:18:31,270 --> 00:18:32,380
I thought coming to the East Sea

361
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:33,820
would let me forget everything.

362
00:18:36,510 --> 00:18:37,580
But today...

363
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,490
Seeing them today,

364
00:18:41,340 --> 00:18:42,380
I realized

365
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:45,660
I'm still all alone.

366
00:18:48,710 --> 00:18:49,770
Why isn't there

367
00:18:49,790 --> 00:18:51,340
another person out there for me?

368
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:54,050
I've been searching all this time.

369
00:18:58,880 --> 00:18:59,970
You'll find someone.

370
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:03,050
At least I still have you to keep me company

371
00:19:03,600 --> 00:19:05,100
and listen to all this nonsense.

372
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:07,180
You're right.

373
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:08,580
It's good you have me.

374
00:19:08,790 --> 00:19:09,860
You won't be alone.

375
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:17,200
[Fanghu Island]

376
00:19:56,790 --> 00:19:57,490
Have you heard?

377
00:19:57,840 --> 00:19:59,420
[Duanming City Inn]
A new man-eating island has appeared.

378
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:01,210
Everyone who goes there gets eaten.

379
00:20:04,990 --> 00:20:06,100
Your eyes aren't healed yet.

380
00:20:06,100 --> 00:20:06,730
Why are you out?

381
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:07,380
Go back.

382
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:08,580
I'm fine.

383
00:20:09,070 --> 00:20:09,820
I'll protect you.

384
00:20:10,310 --> 00:20:10,730
Don't worry.

385
00:20:11,550 --> 00:20:12,450
I'll take care of Tongzhou.

386
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:13,290
You...

387
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:14,180
Lifei!

388
00:20:16,120 --> 00:20:17,860
The invincible evil-repelling talismans.

389
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:20,010
Keep them safe.

390
00:20:21,120 --> 00:20:21,660
Here.

391
00:20:24,120 --> 00:20:24,970
Take them.

392
00:20:30,880 --> 00:20:31,660
What's that smell?

393
00:20:34,310 --> 00:20:35,770
It's drawn with boys' urine.

394
00:20:38,120 --> 00:20:38,820
Guaranteed to work.

395
00:20:41,360 --> 00:20:42,290
Take them.

396
00:20:42,600 --> 00:20:43,450
Keep them safe.

397
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:46,420
I performed a divination this morning before we left.

398
00:20:46,790 --> 00:20:48,340
The signs were really bad.

399
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:50,660
It predicted we'd turn danger into safety,

400
00:20:51,070 --> 00:20:52,900
but one of the divination sticks suddenly broke.

401
00:20:53,310 --> 00:20:54,580
It means gaining and then losing.

402
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:56,010
Very ominous.

403
00:20:58,470 --> 00:20:59,380
What does that mean?

404
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:00,660
It means

405
00:21:00,990 --> 00:21:03,010
even if we make it back safely,

406
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:04,690
we'll still lose something.

407
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,380
Either our souls

408
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,210
or our money.

409
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:08,180
Anyway,

410
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:09,660
keep these on you

411
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:11,100
for protection.

412
00:21:15,710 --> 00:21:16,210
Deng.

413
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:19,100
Where did you get the boys' urine?

414
00:21:27,120 --> 00:21:28,250
A gift from heaven.

415
00:21:32,750 --> 00:21:33,290
It's a summoning signal.

416
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:34,140
Let's go.

417
00:21:51,470 --> 00:21:52,010
Everyone,

418
00:21:52,600 --> 00:21:53,420
this island is strange.

419
00:21:53,750 --> 00:21:54,900
Be extremely careful.

420
00:21:55,230 --> 00:21:56,860
When you split up to search,

421
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:57,530
if anything feels off,

422
00:21:57,840 --> 00:21:58,690
signal immediately.

423
00:21:59,470 --> 00:22:00,180
- Yes. - Yes.

424
00:22:09,710 --> 00:22:10,580
Be careful.

425
00:22:13,120 --> 00:22:13,580
Lifei.

426
00:22:15,030 --> 00:22:15,580
Stay alert.

427
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:37,250
Changyue?

428
00:22:39,640 --> 00:22:40,210
Changyue!

429
00:22:41,510 --> 00:22:42,140
Ye!

430
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:49,820
According to ancient texts,

431
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,140
Fanghu Island

432
00:22:51,160 --> 00:22:52,770
is at least ten thousand years old.

433
00:22:53,470 --> 00:22:54,050
Who knows

434
00:22:54,070 --> 00:22:55,380
