435
00:22:56,070 --> 00:22:56,970
Stay close.

436
00:22:57,440 --> 00:22:58,770
Don't wander off.

437
00:23:03,990 --> 00:23:04,580
Lifei,

438
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,100
is that voice from a male or female?

439
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:08,940
I'm asking you.

440
00:23:09,270 --> 00:23:09,620
Li...

441
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:12,420
Lifei?

442
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:15,420
Lei!

443
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:17,490
We still got separated?

444
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:26,660
Isn't this Qingqiu's phoenix grass?

445
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,010
It grows here too?

446
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:32,140
This place is starting to look more and more like Qingqiu.

447
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:35,730
Xiuyuan!

448
00:23:36,270 --> 00:23:36,820
Tongzhou!

449
00:23:38,360 --> 00:23:39,050
Deng!

450
00:23:52,640 --> 00:23:53,180
Follow me.

451
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:17,970
Why am I back in Qingqiu?

452
00:24:27,640 --> 00:24:28,340
Master?

453
00:24:30,960 --> 00:24:31,660
Xiaobangchui.

454
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:32,770
You call this

455
00:24:32,790 --> 00:24:33,420
watching the place?

456
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:34,940
The radishes are all overgrown.

457
00:24:34,960 --> 00:24:35,820
What a waste.

458
00:24:38,310 --> 00:24:39,250
How are we supposed to eat these?

459
00:24:41,310 --> 00:24:41,900
Master!

460
00:24:42,510 --> 00:24:43,770
You're finally back.

461
00:24:47,550 --> 00:24:48,730
Where have you been all these years?

462
00:24:49,120 --> 00:24:50,770
I've been searching everywhere for you.

463
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:52,860
Kid,

464
00:24:53,600 --> 00:24:55,210
I had business to attend to.

465
00:24:55,230 --> 00:24:56,770
I told you

466
00:24:56,790 --> 00:24:58,380
to go find your senior brother at the academy.

467
00:24:58,640 --> 00:24:59,180
Look at you...

468
00:24:59,510 --> 00:25:00,010
Then you...

469
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:07,210
What a shame about these radishes.

470
00:25:07,640 --> 00:25:08,380
So old.

471
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:09,900
They won't taste good.

472
00:25:10,270 --> 00:25:11,250
What a pity.

473
00:25:11,270 --> 00:25:11,900
They're not old.

474
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:14,050
I'll make you some radish stew.

475
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:18,180
Xiaobangchui!

476
00:25:18,600 --> 00:25:19,770
Xiaobangchui!

477
00:25:19,920 --> 00:25:20,450
Run!

478
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:21,970
Run now!

479
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:25,380
Master.

480
00:25:25,840 --> 00:25:26,420
Master!

481
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,140
Master.

482
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:36,140
Master!

483
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:39,490
Run... Run now!

484
00:25:39,510 --> 00:25:40,180
Master!

485
00:25:43,840 --> 00:25:44,770
Master!

486
00:26:21,120 --> 00:26:21,660
Lifei.

487
00:26:23,310 --> 00:26:24,250
It's me, Lei Xiuyuan.

488
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:28,450
I was before,

489
00:26:29,790 --> 00:26:30,690
and I still am.

490
00:26:33,160 --> 00:26:34,050
You're not Xiuyuan.

491
00:26:34,710 --> 00:26:35,770
Who are you really?

492
00:26:46,270 --> 00:26:47,180
Xiaobangchui.

493
00:26:48,160 --> 00:26:49,140
I am Yecha.

494
00:26:51,030 --> 00:26:51,690
Fake.

495
00:26:53,550 --> 00:26:54,450
It's all fake!

496
00:26:58,200 --> 00:27:00,490
Mind as pure as ice, untouched by a falling sky.

497
00:27:01,070 --> 00:27:03,530
Stay calm through all changes; keep your spirit steady and your mind clear.

498
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:17,250
What the heck is that?

499
00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:20,210
Stop running!

500
00:27:28,790 --> 00:27:30,180
A lump of green mud?

501
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,010
Xiuyuan.

502
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:15,490
Wake up.

503
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:16,770
Xiuyuan.

504
00:28:17,310 --> 00:28:18,140
You are not Yecha.

505
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:19,730
Don't let the demonic force take you.

506
00:28:20,470 --> 00:28:21,140
Xiuyuan!

507
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:14,690
Just a mirage dream!

508
00:30:47,200 --> 00:30:47,820
Lifei?

509
00:30:51,510 --> 00:30:53,420
Did I hurt you again?

510
00:30:54,070 --> 00:30:55,010
You idiot!

511
00:30:56,270 --> 00:30:58,290
You almost got corrupted by demonic force again.

512
00:31:00,070 --> 00:31:02,180
Your resolve has shaken, and your sanity fades.

513
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:04,690
Where's all that training Elder Guangwei gave you?

514
00:31:05,750 --> 00:31:06,820
What happened to all your cultivation?

515
00:31:10,550 --> 00:31:11,820
Where's the evil-repelling talisman Deng gave you?

516
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:13,580
Did you eat it?

517
00:31:26,030 --> 00:31:27,100
From now on,

518
00:31:27,470 --> 00:31:28,340
stay sharp!

519
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:30,140
If you get possessed

520
00:31:30,310 --> 00:31:31,380
by some ghost or demon again,

521
00:31:31,990 --> 00:31:32,450
I...

522
00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:34,180
I'm done with you.

523
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:38,580
You still want me?

524
00:31:42,470 --> 00:31:43,770
Let's get back to Duanming City first,

525
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:45,140
then we'll settle this.

526
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:46,420
Otherwise, I'd be losing out.

527
00:31:47,990 --> 00:31:49,420
Come on, let's find the others.

528
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:01,050
Tongzhou?

529
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:14,940
Tongzhou, congratulations on mastering the Xuanhua Sacred Fire.

530
00:32:15,310 --> 00:32:16,140
From now on,

531
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:17,940
[Ji Tonghe]
no one will dare bully the Yue State.

532
00:32:39,070 --> 00:32:39,660
Lifei?

533
00:32:41,230 --> 00:32:41,860
Lifei!

534
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:48,210
Tonghe?

535
00:32:49,750 --> 00:32:50,340
Tonghe!

536
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:55,860
Tonghe!

537
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:01,420
Tonghe?

538
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:05,340
Mr. Xuanshan?

539
00:33:08,550 --> 00:33:10,180
Mr. Xuanshan!

540
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:29,100
Tong...

541
00:33:29,510 --> 00:33:30,140
Tonghe.

542
00:33:31,070 --> 00:33:31,730
Tonghe.

543
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:47,900
Lifei.

544
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:56,690
No.

545
00:33:58,230 --> 00:33:59,010
Don't go.

546
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:00,340
Lifei!

547
00:34:03,030 --> 00:34:04,380
Don't leave me alone.

548
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:09,490
Lifei...

549
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:25,490
Tongzhou!

550
00:34:33,320 --> 00:34:33,900
Tongzhou.

551
00:34:35,110 --> 00:34:35,700
Tongzhou.

552
00:34:36,190 --> 00:34:36,820
Wake up.

553
00:34:37,840 --> 00:34:38,450
Tongzhou.

554
00:34:40,470 --> 00:34:41,610
Didn't that lump of mud already scatter?

555
00:34:41,630 --> 00:34:42,530
Why isn't he waking up?

556
00:34:43,150 --> 00:34:44,820
Legend says the mirage beast feeds on nightmares.

557
00:34:45,630 --> 00:34:46,530
If the obsession runs too deep,

558
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:48,050
even after the mirage dissipates,

559
00:34:48,190 --> 00:34:48,970
he still won't wake up.

560
00:34:50,590 --> 00:34:51,380
Then what do we do?

561
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:52,970
Is there a way to break it?

562
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:07,530
Tongzhou!

563
00:35:07,720 --> 00:35:08,260
Tongzhou.

564
00:35:09,190 --> 00:35:09,820
Wake up.

565
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:11,530
- Wake up! - Lifei.

566
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:12,900
Lifei.

567
00:35:13,510 --> 00:35:14,700
You're back, Lifei!

568
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:16,380
Lifei.

569
00:35:16,510 --> 00:35:17,260
Alright, alright.

570
00:35:17,590 --> 00:35:18,650
Whatever you just saw,

571
00:35:18,670 --> 00:35:19,380
it wasn't real.

572
00:35:19,550 --> 00:35:20,780
It was all illusions created by the mirage beast.

573
00:35:21,670 --> 00:35:22,340
It wasn't real?

574
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:25,170
All fake?

575
00:35:26,670 --> 00:35:27,420
Are you fake too?

576
00:35:28,470 --> 00:35:29,340
I'm real.

577
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:31,050
When you wouldn't wake up,

578
00:35:31,070 --> 00:35:32,090
I used the Fragrance Bond to come in.

579
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:33,450
Lifei.

580
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:34,700
It's really you?

581
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:36,300
As long as you're real.

582
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:37,610
Don't leave me.

583
00:35:38,400 --> 00:35:39,220
You're all I have now.

584
00:35:39,510 --> 00:35:40,420
Don't leave me.

585
00:35:40,720 --> 00:35:41,820
Never leave me.

586
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:43,610
You're truly all I have now, Lifei.

587
00:35:43,670 --> 00:35:44,260
Tongzhou.

588
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:44,740
Lifei.

589
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:45,220
Tongzhou.

590
00:35:45,240 --> 00:35:46,090
Don't leave me.

591
00:35:46,630 --> 00:35:47,650
- Lifei. - Wake up.

592
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:50,170
- Tongzhou. - Don't...

593
00:35:50,190 --> 00:35:51,340
Don't leave me.

594
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:54,340
Lifei.

595
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:56,380
Don't leave.

596
00:35:56,630 --> 00:35:59,130
Lifei, don't leave me.

597
00:36:00,030 --> 00:36:01,170
Don't leave me, Lifei!

598
00:36:01,190 --> 00:36:01,780
No...

599
00:36:02,190 --> 00:36:03,450
- Don't leave me! - No, Tongzhou!

600
00:36:03,590 --> 00:36:04,780
Don't let yourself be dragged down.

601
00:36:05,470 --> 00:36:06,090
Wake up.

602
00:36:06,400 --> 00:36:07,050
Wake up!

603
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:08,900
Lifei.

604
00:36:09,470 --> 00:36:10,300
Lifei!

605
00:36:17,190 --> 00:36:17,780
Rise.

606
00:36:21,150 --> 00:36:21,780
How are you?

607
00:36:22,190 --> 00:36:22,860
Are you okay?

608
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:33,570
Don't think about it.

609
00:36:34,470 --> 00:36:35,820
It's all because of that lump of mud.

610
00:36:36,150 --> 00:36:37,220
Everything in the dream was fake.

611
00:36:37,670 --> 00:36:38,450
Don't take it to heart.

612
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,380
Someone's there.

613
00:36:45,550 --> 00:36:46,170
Gelin!

614
00:36:46,590 --> 00:36:47,170
Gelin!

615
00:36:49,240 --> 00:36:50,860
Changyue! Ye Ye.

616
00:36:52,150 --> 00:36:52,900
Are you alright?

617
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:54,530
We're fine.

618
00:36:55,190 --> 00:36:55,740
Just

619
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:57,300
saw some strange things.

620
00:36:58,550 --> 00:36:59,340
What did you see?

621
00:37:02,590 --> 00:37:03,530
We restored the Gaolu State,

622
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:04,650
destroyed Longming Sanctuary,

623
00:37:05,630 --> 00:37:06,610
and became great heroes.

624
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:12,940
But

625
00:37:13,590 --> 00:37:14,570
it all vanished quickly.

626
00:37:15,150 --> 00:37:16,220
Just a fleeting dream.

627
00:37:16,550 --> 00:37:17,300
Ended up alone.

628
00:37:17,630 --> 00:37:18,260
Not a good ending.

629
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:19,820
It was all fake.

630
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:21,010
Just an illusion.

631
00:37:21,760 --> 00:37:22,340
Forget it.

632
00:37:25,070 --> 00:37:25,490
Oh,

633
00:37:25,990 --> 00:37:27,220
have any of you seen Gelin?

634
00:37:30,150 --> 00:37:30,780
Gelin!

635
00:37:31,720 --> 00:37:33,610
Gelin!

636
00:37:33,720 --> 00:37:34,340
Gelin!

637
00:37:36,240 --> 00:37:37,340
- Gelin! - Gelin!

638
00:37:38,190 --> 00:37:39,050
Gelin!

639
00:37:45,470 --> 00:37:46,220
Gelin!

640
00:37:47,670 --> 00:37:48,530
Gelin!

641
00:37:52,630 --> 00:37:53,220
Gelin.

642
00:37:58,110 --> 00:37:59,010
- Gelin. - Gelin.

643
00:38:03,470 --> 00:38:04,860
- Gelin! - Gelin!

644
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:07,420
- Gelin. - Gelin.

645
00:38:07,630 --> 00:38:08,530
- Gelin, wake up. - Gelin, wake up.

646
00:38:08,960 --> 00:38:09,650
Wake up.

647
00:38:12,070 --> 00:38:12,970
Ye?

648
00:38:39,030 --> 00:38:40,050
Are you hurt?

649
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:44,900
I...

650
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:55,420
Lu.

651
00:38:56,320 --> 00:38:57,740
Weren't you supposed to stay in Duanming City?

652
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:58,610
Why are you here too?

653
00:39:03,400 --> 00:39:04,570
My master sent me to help.

654
00:39:08,360 --> 00:39:09,610
Lu, you're finally here.

655
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:12,940
Are the other disciples here too?

656
00:39:13,240 --> 00:39:14,220
Take me to them.

657
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:34,050
I'll take you.

658
00:39:39,360 --> 00:39:39,900
Alright.

659
00:39:41,400 --> 00:39:42,300
They can't see you anymore.

660
00:39:48,590 --> 00:39:49,610
Thank you, Lu.

661
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:51,740
How long will you keep up the act?

662
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:56,450
What?

663
00:39:58,070 --> 00:39:59,300
You like Ye Ye, don't you?

664
00:39:59,990 --> 00:40:01,260
Was it for him that you went to end your life

665
00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:02,740
at the cliff?

666
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:09,530
Lu, don't joke.

667
00:40:09,990 --> 00:40:11,170
The one I like is you.

668
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:13,820
You're the one

669
00:40:14,190 --> 00:40:15,860
who's always cold to me.

670
00:40:16,590 --> 00:40:17,490
It really breaks my heart.

671
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:20,300
Are you really into me,

672
00:40:22,240 --> 00:40:23,050
or

673
00:40:24,990 --> 00:40:26,420
am I just a shield?

674
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:37,170
We shouldn't stay here long.

675
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:38,170
Let's go.

676
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:48,380
Are you okay?

677
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:48,900
I'm fine.

678
00:40:53,670 --> 00:40:54,700
Is everyone alright?

679
00:41:02,190 --> 00:41:04,700
Never thought this island held a mirage demon.

680
00:41:05,320 --> 00:41:07,740
They say this beast is treacherous

681
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:09,050
and skilled at creating illusions.

682
00:41:09,190 --> 00:41:10,900
Only those with the strongest will

683
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:12,050
can break through

684
00:41:12,070 --> 00:41:12,900
and slay it.

685
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:15,570
Who managed that?

686
00:41:22,110 --> 00:41:23,050
I'm guessing

687
00:41:24,150 --> 00:41:26,170
it was Deng's evil-repelling talismans that did the trick.

688
00:41:30,670 --> 00:41:31,450
Where's Deng?

689
00:41:41,920 --> 00:41:42,780
Deng!

690
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:45,170
Deng, what happened?

691
00:41:45,630 --> 00:41:46,300
Don't even ask.

692
00:41:47,070 --> 00:41:49,650
I almost got forced into something.

693
00:41:50,070 --> 00:41:50,820
Forced?

694
00:41:55,110 --> 00:41:57,970
Forced to become the head of Wuyue Court.

695
00:41:58,720 --> 00:41:59,780
Becoming the head?

696
00:42:02,550 --> 00:42:03,900
What's wrong with that?

697
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,380
What's good about it?

698
00:42:06,630 --> 00:42:07,900
If you want it, you take it.

699
00:42:07,920 --> 00:42:09,570
- I... - Short-lived and exhausting.

700
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:11,490
Why would I do that to myself?

701
00:42:11,670 --> 00:42:13,420
Isn't it better to sleep in and laze around every day?

702
00:42:14,190 --> 00:42:15,700
Wake up already.

703
00:42:15,720 --> 00:42:17,130
I woke up just in time.

704
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:18,700
If I'd been any slower,

705
00:42:18,720 --> 00:42:20,650
I'd be wearing the head's robe.

706
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:26,860
Qin.

707
00:42:27,470 --> 00:42:28,050
Qin.

708
00:42:28,400 --> 00:42:29,260
What happened to you?

709
00:42:29,800 --> 00:42:31,130
Did you get beaten up in your dream?

710
00:42:38,050 --> 00:42:38,750
[The Eternal Fragrance]

711
00:42:38,750 --> 00:42:40,560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

712
00:42:51,800 --> 00:42:55,480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

713
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:58,480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

714
00:42:58,560 --> 00:43:01,800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

715
00:43:01,800 --> 00:43:05,080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

716
00:43:05,200 --> 00:43:09,080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

717
00:43:09,360 --> 00:43:12,560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

718
00:43:12,720 --> 00:43:18,800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

719
00:43:19,080 --> 00:43:23,200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

720
00:43:23,480 --> 00:43:26,160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

721
00:43:26,360 --> 00:43:28,280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

722
00:43:28,400 --> 00:43:32,720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

723
00:43:32,880 --> 00:43:36,720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

724
00:43:37,080 --> 00:43:40,080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

725
00:43:40,160 --> 00:43:46,280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

726
00:43:46,480 --> 00:43:50,200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

727
00:44:03,440 --> 00:44:07,200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

728
00:44:07,400 --> 00:44:10,200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

729
00:44:10,280 --> 00:44:13,680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

730
00:44:13,680 --> 00:44:17,000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

731
00:44:17,160 --> 00:44:21,000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

732
00:44:21,160 --> 00:44:24,360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

733
00:44:24,600 --> 00:44:30,440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

734
00:44:31,000 --> 00:44:34,920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

735
00:44:35,200 --> 00:44:37,960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

736
00:44:38,160 --> 00:44:40,000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

737
00:44:40,160 --> 00:44:44,360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

738
00:44:44,600 --> 00:44:48,480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

739
00:44:48,720 --> 00:44:51,760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

740
00:44:51,960 --> 00:44:58,680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

741
00:44:58,720 --> 00:45:02,680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

742
00:45:02,920 --> 00:45:05,680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

743
00:45:05,800 --> 00:45:07,720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

744
00:45:07,880 --> 00:45:12,160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

745
00:45:12,360 --> 00:45:16,200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

746
00:45:16,440 --> 00:45:19,560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

747
00:45:19,600 --> 00:45:25,600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

748
00:45:26,000 --> 00:45:30,360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
